Name: Airborne Motocross
About the game: Dash through the tracks and race others to win items. Blow up obstacles with the rocket launcher. Protect yourself with a force field. Defy gravity. Jump. Fly! Use items to speed up your bike. But to make it to the very top of the leaderboards you'll need to get good. Need a break? Then take your time to explore the tracks and follow maps to hidden treasures. Combine items to reach new areas. Use them to overcome obstacles. Unlock new tracks and solve some (optional) physics puzzles along the way. 240+ tracks, leaderboards, tournaments (async PvP). And maybe you'd enjoy some of the challenges. Guide a huge beach ball into the goal. Try to race with your bike shrunk down to the size of a cat, ... .
